channel.title: NO-IP.com problem (DUC)
channel.description:
Hello, I need help with no-ip.com problem.. When i try run it on my vps it just wont connect to server and says error connection to server...
I've tried many fixes but none worked
Who will help me figuring this out will receive something on my server or paypal reward /5 dollars

item.title: NO-IP.com problem (DUC)
item.dc:creator: @Joseph69 Joseph69
item.description:
@Joseph69 wrote:

[quote=“I InDrEk I, post:2, topic:385333”]Go to File>Prefences
And there you should see Network Adapter with drop-down menu.
Try changing the Network adapter and see does it work.
Also try “Use alternative IP Detection method” put a tick there.[/quote]TYSM U FIXED IT FOR ME
